    "description": "在《进击的机甲球》中感受让你肾上腺素飙升的极致肉鸽战斗！你将驾驶着全副武装的机甲，在这个世界展开狂暴轰炸，用你武力在敌人中开辟一条血路！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机甲与球的杀戮舞蹈</h2>在《进击的机甲球》中，你可以享受双重乐趣：操作机甲进行狂轰乱炸，用强大火力把敌人撕成碎片；或化身为弹力十足的球体，在敌军中滚动、弹跳、冲撞，以庞大的动能撞飞敌人。你可以在两种形态间随意无缝切换，用你让人眼花缭乱的操作击败敌军吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/04ab0749fa86886d727af5803e5cdd24.poster.avif?t=1770294881\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/04ab0749fa86886d727af5803e5cdd24.webm?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/04ab0749fa86886d727af5803e5cdd24.mp4?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限乐趣的未知战区</h2>这个游戏世界分为四个大区域，每个区域都有其独特的环境和敌人。随着你的探索，你将遇到越来越多的挑战和更加有趣的地图！冲上坡道，不断弹跳，乘上巨大风扇制造的上升气流，丰富的移动方式让你的战术更为多元化，你将有无数方式击败敌人。发射大量导弹，从地下冒出来给敌军来个突然袭击，或者是如流星一般冲撞地面引发地震……你可以是优雅的蝴蝶，破坏力十足的重型机甲，或是精准狙击的杀手。全看你怎么选择！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/bd5971b5bab65c7b0d810d57758b09b4.poster.avif?t=1770294881\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/bd5971b5bab65c7b0d810d57758b09b4.webm?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/bd5971b5bab65c7b0d810d57758b09b4.mp4?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建你的武器狂潮</h2>你可以灵活运用四种独一无二的持枪机甲，每种机甲都有独特的武器、能力和升级。你还有超过25种不同的武器可供选择，从机枪、霰弹枪到导弹，应有尽有。20多种独特的能力等你来发掘，让你在战场上如鱼得水。构建独属于你的最强战斗Combo吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/a1611ac0a1c97386d141b4a7d3b697c0.poster.avif?t=1770294881\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/a1611ac0a1c97386d141b4a7d3b697c0.webm?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/a1611ac0a1c97386d141b4a7d3b697c0.mp4?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独奏战场交响曲</h2>《进击的机甲球》的每一个动作、每一次射击，都伴随着独特的音效，加上动感十足的背景音乐，你不仅在击败敌人，更是在演奏着一场充满暴力与激情的热血交响乐，每次击溃敌人都像是在空中引爆音符。让每一次战斗变成独属于你的背景音，将敌人击得四分五裂吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/be696f31028fdb70a193ee9b3f1ea240.poster.avif?t=1770294881\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/be696f31028fdb70a193ee9b3f1ea240.webm?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2008510/extras/be696f31028fdb70a193ee9b3f1ea240.mp4?t=1770294881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>做好准备，在《进击的机甲球》中感受技能、策略和混乱的高能结合。终极的冒险正等着你！<br>",
